  <section id="orient">
    <div class="page">

      <div class="head">
        <span class="num">01</span>
        <span class="tag">What it is</span>
      </div>
      <h2>An <span class="ital">extension</span>, not a fork.</h2>
      <p class="standfirst">
        ION is a national commerce network for Indonesia built on the Beckn
        protocol. <code>ion-full.yaml</code> is the contract every participant
        codes against. Its first design decision is the most important one:
        it never embeds Beckn. It points at a local copy of
        <code>beckn.yaml</code> and adds only what Indonesia needs on top.
      </p>

      <figure>
