            <text x="500" y="172" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Newsreader" font-style="italic" font-size="13" fill="#7a6f5e">reference, never copy</text>

            <text x="60" y="40" font-family="Fraunces" font-style="italic" font-size="16" fill="#161513">fig.01</text>
            <text x="60" y="58" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#7a6f5e">two files, run together, merged never</text>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <figcaption>
          <span class="fig">fig. 01</span>
          <span class="cap">Run the two files together through any OpenAPI 3.1.1 validator. When Beckn ships a new version, only beckn.yaml changes — ion.yaml is untouched.</span>
        </figcaption>
