      <p>
        The payoff of this discipline is upgrade safety. Beckn evolves on its own
        clock; Indonesia's regulatory surface evolves on another. Keeping them in
        two files means a Beckn point-release never forces an ION rewrite — and an
        ION policy change never touches the shared protocol core.
      </p>

